    "This is a single-story rectangular office building with dimensions of 30.48 m × 15.24 m (see Fig. 1a).",
    "The building is divided into five zones: four exterior zones and one interior zone.",
    "The average height of the building is 3.048 m and the total surface area is 463.6 m 2.",
    "it is equipped with a packaged Variable Air Volume (VAV), Direct Expansion (DX) cooling coil and gas heating coils, with fully auto-sized input as the HVAC system to be controlled.",
